{ How to continue here? } 10... Qc7 $5 { [%csl Ge5] This has been played in only two games so far. We are preparing to go for the move e5 next following the rule- play on the flank should be countered in the center. } 11. Bf4 { This is necessary but it trades off a pair of minor pieces which is in our favour. } ( 11. e4 { allows } 11... e5 $17 ) ( 11. O-O { is too slow } 11... b5 $15 ) ( 11. Ng5 { is usually a tricky move but does not work here. } 11... h6 12. Nce4 Rd8 13. Bf4 Qa5+ 14. Kf1 { 1-0 (36) Dudin,G (2475) -Kantor,G (2532) Webster Groves 2023 } 14... Nxe4 15. Nxe4 Nf6 $17 ) 11... Bd6 12. Bxd6 Qxd6 { [%cal Gd6e7,Ge6e5,Gb7b5] } *

